## Paper Entry Contract
- Rank
- Overall score (0-100)
- Recommendation
- Title
- Categories
- Innovation Summary (exactly one sentence)
- Why It Matters (2-3 bullets)
- Implementation Angle (2-3 bullets)
- Caveat
- Executive Summary (<=300 words)
- Links to Hugging Face, arXiv, GitHub, and paper resources
- Estimated reading priority
